1
00:01:37,850 --> 00:01:41,000
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,060 --> 00:01:43,930
[Episode 37]

3
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:50,860
How's it going?

4
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,280
Don't worry.

5
00:01:54,930 --> 00:01:57,330
I've found someone
to take the fall for you.

6
00:01:58,910 --> 00:01:59,830
Good.

7
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:02,120
That's good.

8
00:02:03,450 --> 00:02:04,560
Your people, though—

9
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,600
how did they work?

10
00:02:05,620 --> 00:02:06,950
It got found out so fast.

11
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:08,340
And you're one to talk.

12
00:02:08,669 --> 00:02:10,870
The difference you made in the quote
and the construction period was too small.

13
00:02:10,870 --> 00:02:12,530
Who wouldn't get suspicious?

14
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,480
A miss is as good as a mile.

15
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,420
I got careless.

16
00:02:19,020 --> 00:02:19,860
So what now?

17
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:23,090
We'll figure it out as we go.

18
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,800
Let's just close this case first.

19
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:25,410
By the way,

20
00:02:25,690 --> 00:02:27,590
don't come to my place for a while.

21
00:02:27,890 --> 00:02:29,240
We don't want to raise suspicion.

22
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:29,750
I know.

23
00:02:30,820 --> 00:02:32,350
Then my bid...

24
00:02:32,630 --> 00:02:33,560
Alright,

25
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,490
I know what to do.

26
00:02:34,870 --> 00:02:36,000
We'll play it by ear.

27
00:02:39,630 --> 00:02:40,280
Okay.

28
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:44,480
Marcos,

29
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:45,470
I really

30
00:02:46,350 --> 00:02:47,600
let you down.

31
00:02:48,470 --> 00:02:49,880
On behalf of the hotel,

32
00:02:50,030 --> 00:02:53,079
I sincerely apologize
to you and your group.

33
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,880
An apology won't solve the problem now.

34
00:02:58,430 --> 00:02:59,890
Do you understand, Kenny?

35
00:03:01,220 --> 00:03:03,840
Before we have the investigation results,

36
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,620
we will cover all your expenses

37
00:03:05,620 --> 00:03:07,020
during your stay.

38
00:03:07,460 --> 00:03:10,120
I hope you can hold off
on holding us accountable

39
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:12,460
and give us some time to investigate.

40
00:03:13,310 --> 00:03:15,440
I personally trust Miyu's character,

41
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,470
and I don't want to
put you in a difficult position.

42
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:18,920
But this time, Kenny,

43
00:03:19,190 --> 00:03:22,250
I represent the interests
of the entire Liberty Group.

44
00:03:22,460 --> 00:03:23,610
I can't let emotions get in the way.

45
00:03:23,610 --> 00:03:24,300
I'm sorry,

46
00:03:24,910 --> 00:03:27,570
but I need to call the police
as soon as possible.

47
00:03:28,150 --> 00:03:28,800
Marcos,

48
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,190
I promise you.

49
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:32,860
I just need three days.

50
00:03:33,310 --> 00:03:35,400
In three days, I will definitely give you

51
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,730
and Liberty an answer.

52
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,030
Kenny,

53
00:03:38,950 --> 00:03:40,480
This time, you may very well

54
00:03:40,710 --> 00:03:42,970
have to choose between the hotel and her.

55
00:03:44,930 --> 00:03:45,770
I know.

56
00:03:46,870 --> 00:03:47,470
Alright.

57
00:03:48,020 --> 00:03:49,079
Three days, right?

58
00:03:50,210 --> 00:03:51,140
Just three days.

59
00:04:08,980 --> 00:04:10,440
When will you give it to me?

60
00:04:11,180 --> 00:04:13,380
You messed up and you still want a bonus?

61
00:04:13,850 --> 00:04:15,000
Every single thing you asked me to do,

62
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,480
I did right.

63
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:19,310
It's just the Liberty Group
was well prepared.

64
00:04:19,310 --> 00:04:20,839
If you want to blame anyone,

65
00:04:21,089 --> 00:04:24,020
blame yourselves
for walking right into their trap.

66
00:04:25,830 --> 00:04:27,910
Still talking tough. Let me tell you,

67
00:04:28,390 --> 00:04:31,360
they're very unhappy
with how this turned out.

68
00:04:31,830 --> 00:04:33,390
Now that things are messed up,

69
00:04:33,390 --> 00:04:35,070
everything is up in the air.

70
00:04:35,510 --> 00:04:36,390
You'd better think about

71
00:04:36,390 --> 00:04:38,270
how to clean up this mess.

72
00:04:49,290 --> 00:04:57,900
[Purong Hotel]

73
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:51,190
Ms. Xu is very insistent.

74
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:53,630
She said she never
bought a bug,

75
00:04:54,070 --> 00:04:55,680
nor did she plant one

76
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,830
in Mr. Marcos' room.

77
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:58,110
Enough already.

78
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,480
So the bug grew legs

79
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:01,140
and walked in there on its own?

80
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:03,510
But we also checked Ms. Xu's phone.

81
00:05:03,870 --> 00:05:05,800
Her phone has a lock screen passcode.

82
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:06,430
No one but her

83
00:05:06,430 --> 00:05:07,920
can unlock the phone

84
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,320
and pair it with a device.

85
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:11,430
And Ms. Xu herself admitted

86
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:14,440
that she personally delivered the vase

87
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,230
where the bug

88
00:05:16,230 --> 00:05:18,030
was found into Mr. Marcos' room.

89
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:20,480
Why would a salesperson

90
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:23,630
go to a guest's room to deliver a vase?

91
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:24,870
Explain that.

92
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,240
It was a gift Ms. Xu

93
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:29,520
specially prepared for Mr. Marcos.

94
00:05:29,540 --> 00:05:30,890
Marcos knew about it.

95
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:36,250
Did you check Ms. Xu's chat logs

96
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,230
with others?

97
00:05:37,260 --> 00:05:37,920
Yes, I did.

98
00:05:38,350 --> 00:05:41,040
All her communications
with guests were normal.

99
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,560
As for Niu Qiankun,

100
00:05:42,020 --> 00:05:43,860
[Purong Hotel]

101
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,390
whom Mr. Marcos suspects

102
00:05:43,390 --> 00:05:44,630
may be behind this,

103
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:47,720
Ms. Xu doesn't even
have his contact information.

104
00:05:49,870 --> 00:05:50,430
Mr. Ji,

105
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,510
By raising these questions

106
00:05:52,510 --> 00:05:55,120
about motive to obscure
the facts of the crime,

107
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:58,090
are you trying to cover up for a criminal?

108
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:01,530
I'm just stating objective facts.

109
00:06:02,310 --> 00:06:03,240
But you, Mr. Wei,

110
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:05,600
keep calling a hotel employee a criminal

111
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,930
before the chain of evidence's complete.

112
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,510
Could I also assume

113
00:06:09,510 --> 00:06:11,300
that you're framing her on purpose?

114
00:06:11,300 --> 00:06:12,630
That's enough, Ji Feng.

115
00:06:13,890 --> 00:06:15,600
Stop being so hypocritical.

116
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:17,800
Do you think I don't know

117
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:20,000
you're deliberately covering for her?

118
00:06:20,550 --> 00:06:21,920
Everyone

119
00:06:21,940 --> 00:06:24,240
at Purong Hotel knows about

120
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,370
your relationship.

121
00:06:26,540 --> 00:06:27,390
Let me tell you,

122
00:06:27,390 --> 00:06:29,130
you'd better stay out of this.

123
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:30,630
Otherwise, you'll turn everyone
against you,

124
00:06:30,630 --> 00:06:33,230
and you won't even
have your own job to protect.

125
00:06:34,530 --> 00:06:35,040
You.

126
00:06:35,310 --> 00:06:36,870
Xu Miyu was caught red-handed.

127
00:06:36,870 --> 00:06:37,720
Fire her immediately.

128
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,430
Put her on the blacklist

129
00:06:38,430 --> 00:06:40,340
of the National Hotel Association.

130
00:06:40,340 --> 00:06:41,159
Let everyone see

131
00:06:41,159 --> 00:06:43,190
Purong's attitude towards her behavior.

132
00:06:43,190 --> 00:06:45,050
Don't you dare lay a finger on her!

133
00:06:45,320 --> 00:06:46,090
Mr. Ji!

134
00:06:59,340 --> 00:07:00,430
I thought

135
00:07:00,460 --> 00:07:01,920
that with your professionalism,

136
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:04,720
you'd be more calm and composed
at a time like this.

137
00:07:06,870 --> 00:07:08,800
Aunt, you saw all of that, didn't you?

138
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:09,830
But don't worry.

139
00:07:09,830 --> 00:07:11,120
I'm already working on it.

140
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:13,250
I won't let Purong Hotel be disgraced.

141
00:07:13,670 --> 00:07:14,700
Chairwoman,

142
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:16,980
Xu Miyu wouldn't do something like this.

143
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,220
I will take the lead

144
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,600
in forming a board investigative committee

145
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:23,860
to personally investigate this matter.

146
00:07:24,300 --> 00:07:26,910
I will not wrong an innocent person,

147
00:07:27,290 --> 00:07:30,050
but I won't let
any guilty person go either.

148
00:07:30,940 --> 00:07:31,560
Chairwoman—

149
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:34,270
Stay out of this matter.

150
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,680
Don't forget,

151
00:07:36,290 --> 00:07:38,950
you're still
the general manager of this hotel.

152
00:08:10,220 --> 00:08:11,390
The vase you just mentioned

153
00:08:11,390 --> 00:08:13,690
was indeed delivered
by me to Marcos' room.

154
00:08:13,690 --> 00:08:15,690
And I was the only one who handled it.

155
00:08:16,310 --> 00:08:18,240
And Ms. Xu herself admitted

156
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:20,690
that she personally delivered the vase

157
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,480
where the bug

158
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:24,280
was found into Mr. Marcos' room.

159
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:28,840
Where are you going?

160
00:08:28,840 --> 00:08:30,170
The surveillance room.

161
00:08:36,970 --> 00:08:37,440
Hello?

162
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,510
Okay. Got it.

163
00:08:42,309 --> 00:08:44,480
They said the investigation team
will be here soon.

164
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:44,960
Then we probably

165
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,560
won't have time to eat later.

166
00:08:46,750 --> 00:08:48,550
Should we grab a meal first?

167
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:50,160
You're right. Let's go.

168
00:09:17,290 --> 00:09:20,500
[Surveillance Footage]

169
00:09:20,500 --> 00:09:21,040
[Executive Corridor]

170
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:25,410
[Camera 01]

171
00:09:28,110 --> 00:09:31,850
[Camera 01]

172
00:09:33,150 --> 00:09:38,100
[Camera 01]

173
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:44,980
[Camera 01]

174
00:09:47,180 --> 00:09:50,310
[Camera 01]

175
00:09:54,810 --> 00:10:03,840
[Camera 01]

176
00:10:28,730 --> 00:10:30,840
The investigation team is coming
to check the surveillance footage.

177
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,440
I had a feeling you'd be here.

178
00:10:33,930 --> 00:10:34,770
Looks like

179
00:10:35,100 --> 00:10:36,320
Xu Miyu

180
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:38,180
is really being framed this time.

181
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:40,220
I heard

182
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:42,040
it was just some crappy phone app

183
00:10:42,060 --> 00:10:43,260
and a few statements.

184
00:10:43,550 --> 00:10:45,270
If you had stalled them for a few days,

185
00:10:45,270 --> 00:10:47,550
maybe she'd still have a chance.

186
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:50,170
But now with this surveillance footage

187
00:10:49,220 --> 00:10:51,770
[Camera 01]

188
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:52,200
proving that no one entered that room

189
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,930
after the vase was placed in it,

190
00:10:54,270 --> 00:10:55,200
what do we do now?

191
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:58,010
The investigation team
is already upstairs.

192
00:10:58,510 --> 00:10:59,870
With this footage,

193
00:10:59,870 --> 00:11:01,470
it's enough to get her fired.

194
00:11:01,940 --> 00:11:03,180
But it's okay.

195
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:05,150
There's plenty of fish in the sea.

196
00:11:05,150 --> 00:11:06,120
If it doesn't work out,

197
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:08,430
I can transfer a few people from Kuanli

198
00:11:08,460 --> 00:11:09,260
for you to use.

199
00:11:09,260 --> 00:11:10,050
Hurry up.

200
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,500
Taking so long in the bathroom.

201
00:11:11,500 --> 00:11:13,310
The investigation team is almost here.

202
00:11:13,310 --> 00:11:15,430
[Executive Corridor]

203
00:11:13,550 --> 00:11:14,200
Coming, coming.

204
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:14,730
Hurry up.

205
00:11:15,630 --> 00:11:17,380
Y-You're not going to...

206
00:11:17,460 --> 00:11:17,910
[Recycling from Executive Corridor]

207
00:11:17,940 --> 00:11:18,780
[This file is empty]

208
00:11:19,390 --> 00:11:21,150
Are you crazy?
You're throwing away your career.

209
00:11:21,150 --> 00:11:22,550
And deleted files can be recovered.

210
00:11:22,550 --> 00:11:24,350
I need to buy some time right now.

211
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:26,760
The time it takes to recover them

212
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,320
is enough to get to the bottom of this.

213
00:11:27,340 --> 00:11:27,500
[Purong Hotel]

214
00:11:27,580 --> 00:11:28,810
[Recycle Bin]

215
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:35,030
M-Mr. Ji.

216
00:11:39,870 --> 00:11:40,870
Mr. Wang, this way please.

217
00:11:40,870 --> 00:11:41,600
Excuse me.

218
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:45,060
Mr. Duan Jr., you're here too.

219
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:48,150
Mr. Ji, please step aside.

220
00:11:50,070 --> 00:11:51,270
Please wait a moment.

221
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:53,750
I've already had my subordinates

222
00:11:53,750 --> 00:11:55,750
get all the relevant footage ready.

223
00:11:55,750 --> 00:11:56,670
Let me find it.

224
00:11:56,710 --> 00:11:58,510
[Surveillance Footage]
[Executive Corridor]

225
00:12:02,510 --> 00:12:03,190
Where's the footage?

226
00:12:03,190 --> 00:12:04,960
[Executive Corridor]
[This file is empty]

227
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:05,840
I just checked it this morning.
It was fine.

228
00:12:19,490 --> 00:12:20,380
Ji Feng.

229
00:12:21,640 --> 00:12:23,450
You've really got guts.

230
00:12:25,380 --> 00:12:27,240
I'll see you at the board meeting.

231
00:13:55,790 --> 00:13:56,520
Let's begin.

232
00:13:57,510 --> 00:13:58,510
Earlier this year,

233
00:13:58,510 --> 00:14:00,550
Mr. Marcos stayed at the hotel.

234
00:14:01,030 --> 00:14:02,360
Xu Miyu was his butler.

235
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:04,750
She knows Mr. Marcos' habits

236
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:06,950
better than anyone in the hotel.

237
00:14:07,380 --> 00:14:09,190
I did prepare the vase myself.

238
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:12,120
I did run into Ms. Xu in the hallway.

239
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:14,630
She was holding a vase

240
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:17,410
and said she was going to Room 1822.

241
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:20,400
I left right after
I delivered the vase to the room.

242
00:14:21,150 --> 00:14:23,900
I had no idea
there was a bug in the vase.

243
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:25,670
I gave the room card to Miyu.

244
00:14:26,090 --> 00:14:27,840
I was supposed to go with her,

245
00:14:27,980 --> 00:14:29,250
but I got held up at the time

246
00:14:29,250 --> 00:14:31,450
by a guest checking in.

247
00:14:33,550 --> 00:14:34,480
I think...

248
00:14:35,170 --> 00:14:36,890
Miyu wouldn't do such a thing.

249
00:14:36,920 --> 00:14:38,280
Room 1822

250
00:14:38,560 --> 00:14:40,370
has always been cleaned by Dai.

251
00:14:41,230 --> 00:14:42,650
You can go ask her.

252
00:14:42,910 --> 00:14:43,510
Dai?

253
00:14:44,700 --> 00:14:47,710
[Honoring True Hospitality]

254
00:14:44,870 --> 00:14:47,790
After I finished
cleaning the other rooms that day,

255
00:14:48,220 --> 00:14:50,150
I hadn't gotten to Room 1822 yet
when I was called in

256
00:14:50,150 --> 00:14:51,750
to have my phone checked.

257
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:54,700
My other colleagues can prove it.

258
00:14:56,670 --> 00:14:57,870
Anything else to add?

259
00:14:59,510 --> 00:15:04,000
[Honoring True Hospitality]

260
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:08,360
Excuse me,

261
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:10,990
when can I leave?

262
00:15:11,790 --> 00:15:14,030
The hotel has no right
to restrict your freedom.

263
00:15:14,030 --> 00:15:16,000
But until this matter
is fully investigated,

264
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:18,160
you'll be suspended from your duties
and under observation.

265
00:15:18,160 --> 00:15:19,820
And after it's investigated?

266
00:15:20,030 --> 00:15:21,600
Once your actions are confirmed,

267
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:24,000
you could face criminal liability.

268
00:16:18,240 --> 00:16:19,300
Are you okay?

269
00:16:21,020 --> 00:16:21,730
I'm sorry.

270
00:16:22,870 --> 00:16:23,630
I'm fine.

271
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:32,570
I heard from my father

272
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:34,730
that you're in a bad situation.

273
00:16:35,060 --> 00:16:35,860
Is that true?

274
00:16:37,780 --> 00:16:39,150
It's not that bad.

275
00:16:45,020 --> 00:16:45,690
Miyu,

276
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:48,390
come with me.

277
00:16:51,270 --> 00:16:53,930
I don't want you
to face all this danger anymore.

278
00:16:54,660 --> 00:16:55,560
Leave Purong

279
00:16:55,650 --> 00:16:57,250
and come to Hong Kong with me.

280
00:17:02,030 --> 00:17:03,270
Mr. Tan, didn't you decide

281
00:17:03,270 --> 00:17:05,270
to develop your career in Shanghai?

282
00:17:10,450 --> 00:17:12,420
Am I not being clear enough?

283
00:17:13,510 --> 00:17:15,170
Do you really not understand?

284
00:17:15,829 --> 00:17:17,680
It actually doesn't matter where I work.

285
00:17:17,680 --> 00:17:19,339
What matters is where you are.

286
00:17:20,790 --> 00:17:22,270
I don't want you to face

287
00:17:22,270 --> 00:17:25,000
all this workplace politics anymore
just to make a living.

288
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:26,480
I want to protect you.

289
00:17:28,099 --> 00:17:29,510
Let's be together.

290
00:17:31,780 --> 00:17:33,580
Give me a chance, okay?

291
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:37,830
From now on,

292
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:40,850
I won't let anyone hurt you.

293
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:42,960
I will always protect you,

294
00:17:44,150 --> 00:17:46,150
and I'll always protect our family.

295
00:17:46,750 --> 00:17:47,710
I swear.

296
00:17:52,020 --> 00:17:52,980
Thank you.

297
00:17:54,130 --> 00:17:56,610
But I'm sorry.

298
00:17:57,490 --> 00:17:58,550
I can't go with you.

299
00:17:59,920 --> 00:18:01,250
Is it because of Ji Feng?

300
00:18:02,510 --> 00:18:03,440
Not entirely.

301
00:18:05,370 --> 00:18:07,230
Then is it because I came too late?

302
00:18:10,680 --> 00:18:12,380
It's not a matter of timing.

303
00:18:13,830 --> 00:18:15,920
I used to long for the kind of

304
00:18:15,920 --> 00:18:17,980
relationship you're talking about.

305
00:18:19,190 --> 00:18:21,060
But then I realized

306
00:18:22,590 --> 00:18:24,400
that kind of relationship completely

307
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:25,640
entrusting yourself to another person

308
00:18:25,640 --> 00:18:26,790
isn't right for me.

309
00:18:29,750 --> 00:18:30,590
Mr. Tan,

310
00:18:32,620 --> 00:18:34,020
you're a really good man.

311
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:36,550
We just didn't meet

312
00:18:36,550 --> 00:18:37,550
at the right time.

313
00:18:38,710 --> 00:18:40,030
And the future

314
00:18:41,160 --> 00:18:43,000
we want now is different.

315
00:18:50,350 --> 00:18:51,240
Thank you.

316
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:55,060
Thank you for being so honest with me.

317
00:18:56,240 --> 00:18:57,500
I respect your choice.

318
00:19:04,160 --> 00:19:04,770
By the way,

319
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:07,760
did you know Ji Feng has already left

320
00:19:07,760 --> 00:19:08,890
Purong Hotel?

321
00:19:09,380 --> 00:19:10,580
When did that happen?

322
00:19:11,090 --> 00:19:12,090
Just tonight.

323
00:19:16,100 --> 00:19:17,310
My father told me.

324
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:19,160
He deleted

325
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:22,240
the surveillance footage
outside the guest rooms to help you.

326
00:19:22,240 --> 00:19:23,640
The board believed

327
00:19:23,660 --> 00:19:25,710
he was obstructing
the hotel's investigation of you.

328
00:19:25,710 --> 00:19:27,930
And they decided to fire him.

329
00:19:28,810 --> 00:19:31,340
Miyu, they let you go?

330
00:19:31,800 --> 00:19:32,910
Where are you now?

331
00:19:42,210 --> 00:19:44,010
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

332
00:19:45,720 --> 00:19:47,320
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

333
00:19:49,570 --> 00:19:51,400
♪ People in the city ♪

334
00:19:52,310 --> 00:19:55,710
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

335
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:53,960
Are you okay?

336
00:19:54,990 --> 00:19:56,320
Are you out of your mind?

337
00:19:57,180 --> 00:19:59,210
♪ The palms of time ♪

338
00:19:57,470 --> 00:20:00,070
Why did you delete
that surveillance footage?

339
00:20:00,480 --> 00:20:01,650
I didn't mean to.

340
00:20:00,910 --> 00:20:04,210
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

341
00:20:02,610 --> 00:20:03,790
My finger just slipped.

342
00:20:03,790 --> 00:20:05,350
What about your career?

343
00:20:04,650 --> 00:20:07,890
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

344
00:20:05,530 --> 00:20:07,200
Where's your sanity, Ji Feng?

345
00:20:08,020 --> 00:20:10,110
You worked so hard
to get where you are today.

346
00:20:08,580 --> 00:20:10,820
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

347
00:20:10,130 --> 00:20:11,500
I couldn't just stand by and watch them

348
00:20:11,500 --> 00:20:13,360
destroy everything you've done.

349
00:20:15,330 --> 00:20:16,990
So what are you going to do now?

350
00:20:18,960 --> 00:20:19,650
I...

351
00:20:21,030 --> 00:20:22,610
I'll help you find out the truth first,

352
00:20:22,610 --> 00:20:25,130
and we'll figure it out as we go.

353
00:20:26,390 --> 00:20:27,500
How?

354
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:30,170
I've been thinking these days.

355
00:20:31,420 --> 00:20:33,510
From the sales office

356
00:20:33,530 --> 00:20:34,980
to Marcos's room,

357
00:20:35,270 --> 00:20:36,000
no one

358
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:38,030
touched that vase except me.

359
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:40,550
So how did that bug get in there?

360
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:42,790
Did you run into anyone

361
00:20:42,790 --> 00:20:44,070
before you entered the room?

362
00:20:44,070 --> 00:20:45,030
Yes,

363
00:20:45,030 --> 00:20:47,400
but just in passing.

364
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:49,030
None of them had a chance

365
00:20:49,030 --> 00:20:50,480
to plant a bug.

366
00:20:51,570 --> 00:20:53,790
Well, I might have a lead.

367
00:20:54,110 --> 00:20:55,980
I want to look into Wei Siyuan first.

368
00:20:55,980 --> 00:20:56,880
Wei Siyuan?

369
00:20:57,030 --> 00:20:57,680
Why?

370
00:20:57,960 --> 00:20:59,380
Marcos told me

371
00:20:59,430 --> 00:21:00,160
that

372
00:21:00,180 --> 00:21:02,050
Niu Qiankun from Jinkun Group

373
00:21:02,080 --> 00:21:04,270
used to have some dealings
with Wei Siyuan.

374
00:21:04,270 --> 00:21:06,530
So he's definitely involved.

375
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:09,340
And I don't trust
the investigation team either.

376
00:21:09,340 --> 00:21:11,190
I want to follow him myself,

377
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:13,400
see who he's been in contact with.

378
00:21:14,720 --> 00:21:15,780
Wait.

379
00:21:15,880 --> 00:21:18,130
Ms. Xu, what are you doing here?

380
00:21:18,280 --> 00:21:20,710
I need to deliver something to Room 1822.

381
00:21:20,760 --> 00:21:21,690
Are you okay?

382
00:21:21,770 --> 00:21:22,450
I'm fine.

383
00:21:22,480 --> 00:21:23,640
I'll help you pick them up.

384
00:21:23,640 --> 00:21:24,810
Thank you, Ms. Xu.

385
00:21:34,610 --> 00:21:35,870
It just occurred to me—

386
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:37,530
that day in the hallway,

387
00:21:37,560 --> 00:21:39,510
I ran into an attendant named Dai.

388
00:21:39,880 --> 00:21:41,070
She's probably the only other person

389
00:21:41,070 --> 00:21:43,600
who had a chance
to touch that vase besides me.

390
00:21:43,660 --> 00:21:44,900
But I can't figure out

391
00:21:44,920 --> 00:21:46,310
why she would do that.

392
00:21:47,530 --> 00:21:49,730
Let's split up and investigate for now.

393
00:21:51,190 --> 00:21:52,220
And be careful.

394
00:21:54,790 --> 00:21:55,460
Ji Feng,

395
00:21:56,790 --> 00:21:57,680
thank you

396
00:21:58,140 --> 00:22:00,070
for trusting me unconditionally.

397
00:22:01,520 --> 00:22:02,330
Don't worry.

398
00:22:02,830 --> 00:22:04,630
Everything's gonna be alright.

399
00:22:09,510 --> 00:22:10,310
It'll be fine.

400
00:22:11,440 --> 00:22:12,410
It'll be fine.

401
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:28,390
♪ I know at the start of every story ♪

402
00:22:29,320 --> 00:22:31,340
♪ They all feel somewhat the same ♪

403
00:22:33,300 --> 00:22:35,500
♪ Just never thought I would ♪

404
00:22:36,520 --> 00:22:38,500
♪ Fall for you so deeply ♪

405
00:22:40,190 --> 00:22:42,630
♪ Why did I have to lose myself? ♪

406
00:22:43,100 --> 00:22:45,250
♪ In the virtual world ♪

407
00:22:46,600 --> 00:22:51,860
♪ Unfinished dreams hurt the most ♪

408
00:22:53,540 --> 00:22:55,410
♪ Like a moth drawn to the flame ♪

409
00:22:55,950 --> 00:22:59,330
♪ Wandering aimlessly
through the night sky ♪

410
00:23:00,830 --> 00:23:02,420
♪ Until I met you ♪

411
00:23:03,220 --> 00:23:06,390
♪ Like fire that finally took my life ♪

412
00:23:06,920 --> 00:23:08,950
♪ I thought my deep devotion
and sincerity ♪

413
00:23:09,320 --> 00:23:11,050
♪ Would earn your eternal loyalty ♪

414
00:23:11,510 --> 00:23:12,770
♪ Because you are like a cloud ♪

415
00:23:13,140 --> 00:23:14,990
♪ I became a wisp of wind ♪

416
00:23:15,390 --> 00:23:18,390
♪ In the end, all the promises we made ♪

417
00:23:18,610 --> 00:23:20,190
♪ Turned into nothing but emptiness ♪

418
00:23:21,180 --> 00:23:22,960
♪ Once, for your dream ♪

419
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:24,850
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

420
00:23:25,630 --> 00:23:27,830
♪ Love really hurts ♪

421
00:23:29,060 --> 00:23:33,720
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

422
00:24:06,130 --> 00:24:06,890
Qingping.

423
00:24:07,960 --> 00:24:08,770
Ms. Xu?

424
00:24:13,240 --> 00:24:15,310
Ms. Xu, why are you here?

425
00:24:16,410 --> 00:24:17,570
I've been suspended.

426
00:24:17,570 --> 00:24:19,490
So I can't really go upstairs.

427
00:24:19,930 --> 00:24:22,720
Qingping, I want to ask you about someone.

428
00:24:23,330 --> 00:24:26,260
An attendant on the executive floor
named Dai Hui.

429
00:24:26,750 --> 00:24:28,920
The new one, Dai. What about her?

430
00:24:30,890 --> 00:24:33,270
In the days leading up
to the bidding meeting,

431
00:24:33,270 --> 00:24:35,270
did she act strangely?

432
00:24:35,600 --> 00:24:37,310
Like hiding things

433
00:24:37,310 --> 00:24:39,840
or secretly going
through guest belongings?

434
00:24:40,550 --> 00:24:41,960
She's always been hardworking

435
00:24:41,960 --> 00:24:43,110
and honest.

436
00:24:43,130 --> 00:24:44,930
I haven't noticed anything off.

437
00:24:46,310 --> 00:24:48,600
Then who does she usually hang out with?

438
00:24:49,800 --> 00:24:51,590
She's pretty shy.

439
00:24:51,620 --> 00:24:52,750
Besides

440
00:24:52,750 --> 00:24:54,480
the other girls in the HSKP Department,

441
00:24:54,480 --> 00:24:56,680
I haven't seen her close to anyone else.

442
00:24:58,050 --> 00:24:58,770
Oh, right,

443
00:24:58,980 --> 00:25:00,340
when she first came,

444
00:25:00,370 --> 00:25:01,480
I heard someone say

445
00:25:01,850 --> 00:25:03,850
a fellow Ningxin townsman of hers,

446
00:25:03,880 --> 00:25:06,680
who already worked at the hotel,
introduced her.

447
00:25:07,440 --> 00:25:08,110
Who?

448
00:25:08,130 --> 00:25:09,040
I'm not sure.

449
00:25:09,510 --> 00:25:10,440
And even if we asked,

450
00:25:10,440 --> 00:25:11,750
she might not tell us.

451
00:25:14,680 --> 00:25:15,510
What's wrong?

452
00:25:15,930 --> 00:25:17,780
Is it about the bidding meeting?

453
00:25:18,230 --> 00:25:19,630
Do you have any new clues?

454
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:25,070
Miyu,

455
00:25:25,170 --> 00:25:28,050
all of us on the executive floor
believe in you.

456
00:25:28,400 --> 00:25:30,330
If you need us for anything,

457
00:25:30,350 --> 00:25:31,350
just ask.

458
00:25:33,160 --> 00:25:34,720
Thank you, Qingping.

459
00:26:00,200 --> 00:26:01,600
That day at the hospital,

460
00:26:02,960 --> 00:26:04,560
I wanted to say

461
00:26:06,160 --> 00:26:07,360
thank you for coming.

462
00:26:09,410 --> 00:26:10,240
Actually,

463
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:17,610
I'm the one who should be sorry.

464
00:26:20,550 --> 00:26:23,180
Let's not bring up the past.

465
00:26:24,130 --> 00:26:25,340
It's all in the past.

466
00:26:29,840 --> 00:26:32,440
I heard you've run into
some trouble recently.

467
00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:33,530
I'm fine.

468
00:26:34,760 --> 00:26:35,570
I know.

469
00:26:36,550 --> 00:26:37,480
I don't have the right to ask.

470
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:38,510
I'm really fine.

471
00:26:43,940 --> 00:26:45,280
Take care of yourself.

472
00:26:46,530 --> 00:26:47,330
Wait a minute.

473
00:26:50,830 --> 00:26:52,360
Actually, I came here today

474
00:26:52,830 --> 00:26:54,420
to tell you something.

475
00:26:57,870 --> 00:26:59,670
When I got home from the hospital

476
00:27:00,440 --> 00:27:01,920
to pack my things,

477
00:27:02,330 --> 00:27:04,930
I saw Lu Zhenzhen
on the phone with your sister.

478
00:27:06,250 --> 00:27:07,860
You must be surprised too.

479
00:27:09,150 --> 00:27:11,610
Those two have nothing
to do with each other.

480
00:27:11,960 --> 00:27:13,490
They talked for a long time.

481
00:27:14,110 --> 00:27:15,510
Something just felt off.

482
00:27:20,160 --> 00:27:22,440
-Open the door! I know you're inside!
-Yao Zhigang's not home!

483
00:27:22,440 --> 00:27:24,480
-He took off!
-Open the door!

484
00:27:24,480 --> 00:27:25,590
Pay up, Yao Zhigang!

485
00:27:25,590 --> 00:27:27,910
-I really have no money.
-Go!

486
00:27:28,350 --> 00:27:29,960
Don't come to me anymore!

487
00:27:29,960 --> 00:27:30,680
I have no money!

488
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:31,480
Stop it!

489
00:27:32,980 --> 00:27:34,310
I've called the police.

490
00:27:42,640 --> 00:27:43,240
Tell me.

491
00:27:44,840 --> 00:27:46,100
Is it because of money?

492
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:49,590
What money?

493
00:27:51,970 --> 00:27:54,260
How much do you owe those people?

494
00:27:54,510 --> 00:27:56,640
That's not even my debt.

495
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:58,310
It's that bastard, Yao Zhigang.

496
00:27:58,310 --> 00:27:59,880
He racked up a huge debt,

497
00:27:59,880 --> 00:28:01,310
and then disappeared.

498
00:28:01,310 --> 00:28:02,480
What a scumbag.

499
00:28:03,720 --> 00:28:05,960
Tell me, was it that night?

500
00:28:08,310 --> 00:28:09,830
W-What night?

501
00:28:12,720 --> 00:28:14,640
You came to my dorm that night,

502
00:28:14,640 --> 00:28:17,110
pretending to ask about the guesthouse,

503
00:28:17,880 --> 00:28:19,400
but you were really trying

504
00:28:19,400 --> 00:28:20,720
to install that bugging app on my phone,

505
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:21,550
weren't you?

506
00:28:22,350 --> 00:28:23,240
W-What?

507
00:28:23,240 --> 00:28:24,460
What... What app?

508
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:25,680
Install what?

509
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:27,940
I have no idea what you're talking about.

510
00:28:28,590 --> 00:28:30,110
It's fine if you don't admit it.

511
00:28:30,110 --> 00:28:32,070
But I'm telling you,

512
00:28:32,070 --> 00:28:33,240
you didn't succeed.

513
00:28:33,260 --> 00:28:35,520
All that work for nothing, you know that?

514
00:28:35,720 --> 00:28:37,530
Don't try to bluff me here.

515
00:28:37,590 --> 00:28:38,640
Use your brain.

516
00:28:38,640 --> 00:28:39,970
If you had succeeded,

517
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:42,660
would I be sitting here
in front of you right now?

518
00:28:48,190 --> 00:28:49,580
Did you get the money?

519
00:28:53,350 --> 00:28:54,440
I can tell you this—

520
00:28:54,800 --> 00:28:56,460
you're not getting the money.

521
00:28:56,640 --> 00:28:58,510
It's because they're
looking for idiots like you

522
00:28:58,510 --> 00:29:00,350
who work for free.

523
00:29:00,400 --> 00:29:02,350
Bullshit! She promised me!

524
00:29:02,350 --> 00:29:04,000
As long as I installed that app—

525
00:29:04,000 --> 00:29:04,510
Who?

526
00:29:12,960 --> 00:29:14,400
You can keep your mouth shut.

527
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:15,920
Let the masterminds speak for you

528
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:17,410
while you go to jail for them.

529
00:29:17,410 --> 00:29:18,440
Fair trade.

530
00:29:18,590 --> 00:29:19,740
Everyone wins.

531
00:29:20,900 --> 00:29:21,550
No.

532
00:29:23,410 --> 00:29:25,480
Wait, don't go.

533
00:29:25,720 --> 00:29:27,550
I'll tell you, okay?

534
00:30:09,000 --> 00:30:09,970
I'm leaving.

535
00:30:13,880 --> 00:30:14,800
Take care.

536
00:30:38,250 --> 00:30:40,020
[oume Mountain Dinner]

537
00:30:42,640 --> 00:30:45,590
I've seen many women like you.

538
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:48,350
You think you can come after my husband

539
00:30:50,350 --> 00:30:52,480
just because you've got a pretty face?

540
00:30:53,510 --> 00:30:55,400
It's laughable.

541
00:30:55,450 --> 00:30:56,820
Who do you think you are?

542
00:30:56,880 --> 00:30:58,510
I have to deal with at least

543
00:30:58,530 --> 00:31:00,000
10 women like you every year

544
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:01,610
for my husband.

545
00:31:01,680 --> 00:31:02,930
[Come to Shanghai Landmark]

546
00:31:01,830 --> 00:31:03,750
Lu Zhenzhen somehow found out

547
00:31:03,010 --> 00:31:05,490
[Xu Miyu] [Lu Zhenzhen]
[Unknown relationship]

548
00:31:03,750 --> 00:31:05,790
about Yao Zhigang's gambling debts.

549
00:31:05,790 --> 00:31:07,160
She came straight to me

550
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:09,270
and said she had a great way for me
to make money.

551
00:31:09,270 --> 00:31:11,880
She wanted me to install
the transmitting software

552
00:31:11,880 --> 00:31:13,200
for a bug onto your phone.

553
00:31:13,200 --> 00:31:16,480
Once they won the bid,
she'd give me 500,000

554
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:17,920
to pay off my debts.

555
00:31:18,070 --> 00:31:19,640
You saw it today too.

556
00:31:19,640 --> 00:31:21,400
Those debt collectors
are at my door every day.

557
00:31:21,400 --> 00:31:23,790
I can't live like this anymore.

558
00:31:23,920 --> 00:31:24,720
The thought of

559
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:27,270
making 500,000 so easily

560
00:31:27,270 --> 00:31:28,750
just got the better of me.

561
00:31:28,750 --> 00:31:30,190
I'm sorry, Miyu.

562
00:31:30,270 --> 00:31:32,400
I'm begging you,
please don't call the police.

563
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:34,270
Lu Zhenzhen tricked me

564
00:31:34,270 --> 00:31:35,530
into this.

565
00:31:35,640 --> 00:31:36,440
I'm fine.

566
00:31:36,920 --> 00:31:38,780
At least we have another clue now.

567
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:41,940
It's pretty clear now.

568
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:44,200
Lu Zhenzhen used your sister

569
00:31:44,220 --> 00:31:45,420
to set you up.

570
00:31:46,270 --> 00:31:47,400
And considering

571
00:31:47,590 --> 00:31:49,720
how Wei Siyuan's wife
cursed her out to her face,

572
00:31:49,720 --> 00:31:52,110
there's clearly some special relationship

573
00:31:51,010 --> 00:31:54,950
[Xu Miyu] [Lu Zhenzhen] [Wei Siyuan]

574
00:31:52,110 --> 00:31:54,140
between her and Wei Siyuan.

575
00:31:54,180 --> 00:31:55,090
But

576
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:57,030
I still think

577
00:31:57,510 --> 00:32:00,240
someone else planted the bug.

578
00:32:02,140 --> 00:32:03,380
[Xu Miyu] [Lu Zhenzhen]
[Wei Siyuan] [Unknown relationship]

579
00:32:03,480 --> 00:32:04,680
You didn't see Lu Zhenzhen

580
00:32:04,680 --> 00:32:06,340
on the surveillance footage,

581
00:32:06,440 --> 00:32:08,200
and she never touched the vase.

582
00:32:08,800 --> 00:32:11,140
Whoever planted it is key.

583
00:32:11,400 --> 00:32:13,030
Either she's connected to Lu Zhenzhen

584
00:32:13,030 --> 00:32:14,720
or to Wei Siyuan.

585
00:32:16,350 --> 00:32:17,240
By the way, how's the investigation

586
00:32:17,240 --> 00:32:19,170
on the person you suspected going?

587
00:32:19,920 --> 00:32:21,480
I still can't find her connection

588
00:32:21,480 --> 00:32:23,830
to Lu Zhenzhen and Wei Siyuan.

589
00:32:24,100 --> 00:32:26,190
Let's think about it differently.

590
00:32:27,510 --> 00:32:29,200
This kind of risky dirty work

591
00:32:29,200 --> 00:32:31,330
must be done by someone controllable.

592
00:32:31,920 --> 00:32:33,510
If I were the mastermind,

593
00:32:34,310 --> 00:32:36,310
I'd pick someone with a connection,

594
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:37,510
but not someone

595
00:32:37,510 --> 00:32:38,960
who stood out too much.

596
00:32:40,350 --> 00:32:41,600
When she first came,

597
00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:42,920
I heard someone say

598
00:32:43,220 --> 00:32:44,160
a fellow Ningxin townsman of hers,

599
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:46,350
who already worked at the hotel,

600
00:32:46,590 --> 00:32:47,790
introduced her.

601
00:32:47,810 --> 00:32:48,550
Now that you mention it,

602
00:32:48,550 --> 00:32:50,080
something comes to my mind.

603
00:32:50,720 --> 00:32:52,470
Lu Zhenzhen is from Ningxin.

604
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:54,070
So is she.

605
00:32:54,920 --> 00:32:56,160
Luo Qingping said earlier

606
00:32:56,160 --> 00:32:58,130
she was introduced by a fellow townsman.

607
00:32:58,130 --> 00:33:00,530
Could that fellow townsman be Lu Zhenzhen?

608
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:09,640
Hello, Qingping?

609
00:33:10,280 --> 00:33:11,780
Can you do me a favor?

610
00:33:10,660 --> 00:33:15,410
[Xu Miyu] [Lu Zhenzhen]
[Wei Siyuan] [Unknown relationship]

611
00:33:19,070 --> 00:33:20,160
Everyone,

612
00:33:19,970 --> 00:33:21,080
[Purong Hotel]

613
00:33:21,130 --> 00:33:23,790
please write down
your schedule from last week,

614
00:33:23,840 --> 00:33:26,290
along with every person
you came into contact with

615
00:33:26,290 --> 00:33:27,770
and all the details.

616
00:33:29,450 --> 00:33:31,540
No whispering while writing.

617
00:33:42,400 --> 00:33:43,240
Dai.

618
00:33:45,510 --> 00:33:46,400
What's wrong?

619
00:33:47,100 --> 00:33:48,480
You look terrible.

620
00:33:48,510 --> 00:33:49,320
I'm fine.

621
00:33:49,920 --> 00:33:51,300
Are you sick?

622
00:33:51,920 --> 00:33:53,350
No, I'm fine.

623
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:55,680
You need to be completely honest.

624
00:33:55,680 --> 00:33:57,590
Write down every detail clearly.

625
00:33:57,830 --> 00:33:59,030
Do not hide anything,

626
00:33:59,350 --> 00:34:02,480
or there will be severe consequences.

627
00:34:04,570 --> 00:34:08,380
[Purong Hotel]

628
00:34:24,870 --> 00:34:31,190
[Monday]

629
00:34:38,650 --> 00:34:42,860
[Monday, I got up...]

630
00:34:50,300 --> 00:34:54,139
[Monday, I got up at 6 a.m.]

631
00:34:58,550 --> 00:35:00,230
[Monday, I got up at 6 a.m.]

632
00:35:04,020 --> 00:35:05,590
[Monday, I got up at 6 a.m.]

633
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:16,040
Dai, what's wrong?

634
00:35:16,040 --> 00:35:17,030
You can talk to me.

635
00:35:17,030 --> 00:35:18,430
Don't keep it bottled up.

636
00:35:21,320 --> 00:35:22,660
I didn't mean to.

637
00:35:22,710 --> 00:35:24,680
I really didn't mean to.

638
00:35:30,100 --> 00:35:36,720
[General Manager's Office]

639
00:35:31,060 --> 00:35:31,710
Ms. Lu.

640
00:35:31,710 --> 00:35:32,510
You can't go in.

641
00:35:32,510 --> 00:35:33,360
If you don't have an appointment,

642
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:34,510
you can't just go in.

643
00:35:34,510 --> 00:35:35,320
Ms. Lu.

644
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:36,030
Ms. Lu.

645
00:35:39,610 --> 00:35:41,510
Why are you barging into my office?

646
00:35:41,510 --> 00:35:42,510
Are you out of your mind?

647
00:35:42,510 --> 00:35:43,590
This is a critical time right now.

648
00:35:43,590 --> 00:35:45,090
Aren't you giving them
something against us?

649
00:35:45,090 --> 00:35:46,240
I had no choice.

650
00:35:46,270 --> 00:35:47,330
I wanted to see you,

651
00:35:47,440 --> 00:35:48,990
but you sent your wife

652
00:35:49,010 --> 00:35:51,480
and threatened
to kick me out of Purong Hotel.

653
00:35:51,480 --> 00:35:53,140
I have to come beg you, Mr. Wei.

654
00:35:53,150 --> 00:35:55,030
Please, let me keep my job.

655
00:35:55,110 --> 00:35:56,470
My wife went to see you?

656
00:35:56,560 --> 00:35:57,780
I had no idea.

657
00:35:59,760 --> 00:36:02,490
Someone in the company
must have gossiped to her.

658
00:36:02,630 --> 00:36:03,510
Don't be mad.

659
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:05,570
Once things settle down
here in a couple of days,

660
00:36:05,570 --> 00:36:07,420
I'll definitely find you another job.

661
00:36:07,420 --> 00:36:08,410
Bbetter than Purong.

662
00:36:08,410 --> 00:36:09,250
Okay?

663
00:36:10,300 --> 00:36:12,030
Don't treat me like a naive girl.

664
00:36:12,030 --> 00:36:13,760
I can quit.

665
00:36:14,280 --> 00:36:15,800
But first, give me the money you promised.

666
00:36:15,800 --> 00:36:17,190
Didn't I tell you?

667
00:36:17,210 --> 00:36:18,590
Until this bidding thing gets settled,

668
00:36:18,590 --> 00:36:19,960
they're not paying me.

669
00:36:20,040 --> 00:36:21,110
You're pushing me so hard now.

670
00:36:21,110 --> 00:36:22,240
How can I give you anything?

671
00:36:22,240 --> 00:36:23,490
If you don't give me money,

672
00:36:23,490 --> 00:36:24,930
how am I supposed to raise the child

673
00:36:24,930 --> 00:36:26,490
and pay the mortgage?

674
00:36:26,650 --> 00:36:27,800
Wei Siyuan, let me tell you,

675
00:36:27,800 --> 00:36:28,360
I can do anything

676
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:29,110
for this child.

677
00:36:29,110 --> 00:36:30,190
Don't push me.

678
00:36:33,510 --> 00:36:34,240
Zhenzhen,

679
00:36:34,630 --> 00:36:36,110
that's my child too.

680
00:36:37,400 --> 00:36:39,070
You're the mother of my child.

681
00:36:39,400 --> 00:36:41,530
How could I not take care of both of you?

682
00:36:42,210 --> 00:36:43,590
Don't be so glib with me!

683
00:36:43,660 --> 00:36:44,790
Alright. Come here.

684
00:36:45,710 --> 00:36:47,390
Let's solve the problem.

685
00:36:47,410 --> 00:36:48,850
No need to be angry.

686
00:36:49,550 --> 00:36:50,360
Tell me.

687
00:37:02,740 --> 00:37:04,860
Lu Zhenzhen. Stop!

688
00:37:07,230 --> 00:37:08,230
Didn't I tell you?

689
00:37:08,230 --> 00:37:09,440
Just wait.

690
00:37:09,440 --> 00:37:10,760
Why did you come here?

691
00:37:10,760 --> 00:37:11,730
Wait?

692
00:37:12,070 --> 00:37:13,590
If we wait any longer,
my husband will be dead,

693
00:37:13,590 --> 00:37:15,110
and our house will be torn down!

694
00:37:15,110 --> 00:37:16,480
We had a deal.

695
00:37:16,480 --> 00:37:17,550
As soon as the bidding meeting was over,

696
00:37:17,550 --> 00:37:18,840
you'd give me the money immediately.

697
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:19,920
It's been days now.

698
00:37:19,920 --> 00:37:20,970
Where's the money?

699
00:37:20,970 --> 00:37:22,700
I'm warning you, Lu Zhenzhen.

700
00:37:22,730 --> 00:37:23,880
If you don't give me the money now,

701
00:37:23,880 --> 00:37:25,030
next time the debt collectors come,

702
00:37:25,030 --> 00:37:26,890
I'll bring them right here to you.

703
00:37:27,820 --> 00:37:29,300
There's nothing I can do.

704
00:37:29,360 --> 00:37:31,190
They still haven't paid me yet.

705
00:37:31,190 --> 00:37:32,440
I'm anxious too.

706
00:37:32,550 --> 00:37:34,710
Miyao, can you just give me two more days?

707
00:37:34,710 --> 00:37:35,630
As soon as I get the money,

708
00:37:35,630 --> 00:37:36,510
I'll transfer it to you immediately.

709
00:37:36,510 --> 00:37:38,010
Not a cent less.

710
00:37:39,070 --> 00:37:41,070
Do you think I'll still believe you?

711
00:37:41,190 --> 00:37:42,920
You've said that so many times.

712
00:37:43,190 --> 00:37:44,070
Here's the deal.

713
00:37:44,070 --> 00:37:45,800
Write it down in black and white today,

714
00:37:45,800 --> 00:37:48,000
so you won't back out later. Let's go.

715
00:37:48,510 --> 00:37:49,360
Hey,

716
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:50,000
what are you doing?

717
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:50,670
Let's go!

718
00:38:01,430 --> 00:38:03,640
Did you install the bugging app,

719
00:38:03,670 --> 00:38:04,980
or did your sister?

720
00:38:05,030 --> 00:38:05,880
I don't know.

721
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:07,630
Anyway, it wasn't me.

722
00:38:07,650 --> 00:38:09,300
Stop framing me, okay?

723
00:38:10,070 --> 00:38:11,230
What do you mean?

724
00:38:11,440 --> 00:38:12,670
Didn't you come to me

725
00:38:12,670 --> 00:38:14,320
and ask me to get Miyu's phone

726
00:38:14,320 --> 00:38:15,510
and install that bugging app

727
00:38:15,510 --> 00:38:17,070
in exchange for 500,000?

728
00:38:17,070 --> 00:38:18,360
You're trying to deny it now?

729
00:38:18,360 --> 00:38:19,070
Ma'am,

730
00:38:19,280 --> 00:38:20,880
you've got the wrong person.

731
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:22,360
I don't even know you, okay?

732
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:23,670
Do you think I'm three years old?

733
00:38:23,670 --> 00:38:25,030
I've got the wrong person?

734
00:38:25,030 --> 00:38:26,320
If you hadn't come to me,

735
00:38:26,320 --> 00:38:27,880
would I have ever come up with
such a despicable scheme

736
00:38:27,880 --> 00:38:29,070
to harm my own sister?

737
00:38:29,070 --> 00:38:30,670
-I'm asking you, are you even human?
-Miyao.

738
00:38:30,670 --> 00:38:31,200
Sit down.

739
00:38:31,230 --> 00:38:32,880
Don't act like a shrew here, okay?

740
00:38:32,880 --> 00:38:35,280
-Who are you calling a shrew?
-Lu Zhenzhen.

741
00:38:36,190 --> 00:38:37,190
If you don't want others to know,

742
00:38:37,190 --> 00:38:38,720
you shouldn't have done it.

743
00:38:38,920 --> 00:38:41,190
Don't think that just because you deny it,

744
00:38:41,190 --> 00:38:43,800
the bad things you've done
will just disappear.

745
00:38:43,800 --> 00:38:46,320
I don't have time
to deal with you two right now.

746
00:38:46,320 --> 00:38:48,120
I need to go home and feed my baby.

747
00:38:48,320 --> 00:38:49,030
-You can't leave.
-I'm leaving.

748
00:38:49,030 --> 00:38:49,880
-You can't leave!
-I need to go feed my baby.

749
00:38:49,880 --> 00:38:50,840
Wait a minute.

750
00:38:52,630 --> 00:38:53,190
Great.

751
00:38:53,590 --> 00:38:55,920
You brought your boyfriend here too, huh?

752
00:38:56,110 --> 00:38:58,190
Are the three of you trying to set me up?

753
00:38:58,190 --> 00:38:58,880
Ms. Lu,

754
00:39:00,370 --> 00:39:01,770
take a look at this first.

755
00:39:06,710 --> 00:39:07,280
[I'm Dai Hui, an attendant
on the executive floor of Purong Hotel.]

756
00:39:07,300 --> 00:39:07,810
[Not long ago, Lu Zhenzhen,
the fellow townsman who helped me]

757
00:39:07,830 --> 00:39:08,460
[get this job, asked me
to plant a bug in a guest's room.]

758
00:39:09,980 --> 00:39:11,380
I don't know this person.

759
00:39:11,750 --> 00:39:12,880
I don't know what she's talking about.

760
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:13,940
You don't know her?

761
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:15,320
Are you sure you're not the one

762
00:39:15,320 --> 00:39:17,320
who introduced her to Purong Hotel?

763
00:39:17,510 --> 00:39:18,190
No.

764
00:39:19,630 --> 00:39:20,630
I don't know who this person is.

765
00:39:20,630 --> 00:39:22,760
And I don't know what she wrote either.

766
00:39:23,510 --> 00:39:24,710
Then what about this?

767
00:39:24,980 --> 00:39:27,030
[How to Use the Bug] [Start Recording]

768
00:39:25,320 --> 00:39:26,730
This is the guide you gave Dai Hui

769
00:39:26,730 --> 00:39:28,590
to teach her how to turn on the bug.

770
00:39:29,120 --> 00:39:29,930
Remember?

771
00:39:30,250 --> 00:39:32,430
You're not the general manager
of Purong Hotel anymore.

772
00:39:32,430 --> 00:39:34,000
Don't wave a piece of paper at me

773
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:35,000
that could be printed

774
00:39:35,000 --> 00:39:38,350
-at any copy shop here...
-Other than Dai Hui's fingerprints,

775
00:39:38,350 --> 00:39:40,320
the rest of the prints on this
should be yours.

776
00:39:40,320 --> 00:39:41,820
If I give this to the police,

777
00:39:41,820 --> 00:39:43,420
they'll give us the truth.

778
00:39:43,710 --> 00:39:44,510
Lu Zhenzhen,

779
00:39:45,030 --> 00:39:46,170
no one in this world

780
00:39:46,710 --> 00:39:48,510
can live in a vacuum.

781
00:39:49,630 --> 00:39:52,450
Everything you do leaves a trace.

782
00:39:53,000 --> 00:39:55,730
Do you need me
to call Dai Hui over to confront you?

783
00:40:00,560 --> 00:40:01,410
No need.

784
00:40:05,190 --> 00:40:06,030
I admit it.

785
00:40:07,070 --> 00:40:08,370
I asked Dai Hui

786
00:40:08,390 --> 00:40:10,230
to put the bug in the vase.

787
00:40:10,920 --> 00:40:11,710
I

788
00:40:12,230 --> 00:40:13,320
asked your sister

789
00:40:14,110 --> 00:40:16,920
to install the bugging app on your phone.

790
00:40:18,280 --> 00:40:19,630
Are you happy now?

791
00:40:21,920 --> 00:40:23,080
Why did you do that?

792
00:40:23,320 --> 00:40:24,520
Because I need money.

793
00:40:25,230 --> 00:40:26,950
How much did Wei Siyuan promise you?

794
00:40:26,950 --> 00:40:27,810
Eight million.

795
00:40:27,820 --> 00:40:30,480
And you were only
going to give me half a million?

796
00:40:30,590 --> 00:40:31,670
How ruthless.

797
00:40:33,110 --> 00:40:35,240
I need to buy an apartment in Shanghai.

798
00:40:36,070 --> 00:40:37,670
This is the exact amount I need.

799
00:40:37,670 --> 00:40:39,400
I need to give my child a future.

800
00:40:39,630 --> 00:40:40,630
You need money?

801
00:40:40,630 --> 00:40:41,510
Who doesn't?

802
00:40:41,510 --> 00:40:42,630
Don't I need money?

803
00:40:42,630 --> 00:40:44,840
Needing money is no excuse
for doing what you did.

804
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:47,440
I know nothing I say now
will make a difference,

805
00:40:49,280 --> 00:40:50,810
but that's the whole truth.

806
00:40:50,880 --> 00:40:52,210
What about that guy Nie?

807
00:40:55,840 --> 00:40:56,800
We got divorced.

808
00:41:00,070 --> 00:41:01,270
What about the child?

809
00:41:04,730 --> 00:41:06,190
The child is Wei Siyuan's.

810
00:41:19,120 --> 00:41:20,610
[Meeting Room]

811
00:41:21,530 --> 00:41:22,520
[Mr. Wei]
